Lunch that deserves a standing ovation 👏✨

Tucked away in the heart of Hyderabad, @kokohyderabad is rewriting the rules of Asian luxury dining — and their new Chef’s Special Menu (on till June 30) is proof that every detail matters.

From the fiery Spicy Lamb Mala Style to the buttery Sichuan Lobster Dumplings and their signature Pork Lapchong & Smoked Tenderloin Rice — each dish was a masterclass in balance, texture, and bold flavour.

Whether you’re a dim sum devotee or just in for the vibe, trust me — this one’s worth the hype. 🍜💥

🥢 Highly recommend: Go for lunch, go hungry, and go before June 30 😉

@boldbeyond.agency

You change your bedsheets regularly, but when was the last time you actually cleaned your mattress? 👀

Let me break it to you—your mattress is home to dust, dead skin cells, mites, and all the things you’d rather not be lying on 😬
But thanks to the Dyson, deep cleaning has become SO easy and effective.

It’s honestly the best thing I’ve done for my sleep (and my skin!) lately 🛏✨

Welcome to a new era of intimate & Postpartum care for women at 9M Hospital by Ankura!

This is India’s first dedicated Reconstructive and Cosmetic Gynecology Department in a comprehensive hospital setup - women-focused environment that prioritizes comfort, confidence, and care.

Whether it’s changes after childbirth, Menopause, or health-related concerns, this department offers advanced treatments designed to help women feel empowered in their bodies.

From vaginal tightening to labiaplasty, each service blends function and aesthetics, including a special postpartum makeover program called “NewMomMe”.

All procedures are performed with the utmost care and safety by Dr. Pratibha Narayan, using the latest cutting-edge technology.

Got questions? Reach out to 9M Hospital by Ankura today.
